| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2854 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 296ea329-d297-58f2-a8dc-44c5e8b652c6"
